<%# 2026-05-11 polish (Fix 2) — colored bold rating badge.
    Renders a bold `<span class="game-rating-badge game-rating-badge--<tier>">`
    with inline `color:` sourced from the per-tier CSS variable. Missing
    ratings render a muted em-dash inside the same span so layout stays
    consistent across rows. %>
<% if present? %>
<span class="game-rating-badge game-rating-badge--<%= tier %>"
      style="color: <%= css_color %>; font-weight: bold;"
      data-tier="<%= tier %>"
      data-rating="<%= rating %>"><%= display_text %></span>
<% else %>
<span class="game-rating-badge game-rating-badge--missing text-muted"
      data-tier="missing"><%= missing_glyph %></span>
<% end %>
